{"tid":909834,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"支持含大五人幫！","createTime":"2018-11-20T16:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T14:48:11.000Z","uid":219183,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a95e1199625e57d88c517411ee136d8f5e99d4c0","tid":909834,"uid":219183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:40:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我今天是作為一個FM跟你們講的。你們連登仔千萬要注意啊，不要「見著風，是得雨」啊。我感覺你們連登仔還要學習一個，你們非常熟悉公平這一套的 value（價值）。你們畢竟還 too young（太年輕），明白我的意思吧。我告訴你們我是身經百戰了，見得多了！啊，含大的哪一個學系我去過？師兄他們&mdash;&mdash;你&hellip;&hellip;你們要知道，含管的烏大龜，那比你們不知道高到哪裏去了。啊，我跟他談笑風生！所以說連登仔啊，要&hellip;&hellip;還是要提高自己的知識水平！懂我的意思啊！你們有一個好，全世界跑到什麼地方，你們比其他的廢青毒撚啊，跑得還快。但是呢，問來問去的問題啊，都 too simple（太膚淺），啊，sometimes na&iuml;ve!（有時很幼稚！）計contribution也要按照基本法的。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n利申：(含大生)冇條件支持五人組打壓樓主既伸冤行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6b37a827a13ed103fa9acff6646e54cde567b3","tid":909834,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:41:02.000Z","msg":"OK"},{"pid":"19de4901cc10b107ad799cd5640508a933273e9d","tid":909834,"uid":200521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"兒登仔應該唔識老江呢個梗"},{"pid":"3f5a61be73a7b22edb904a577402b4b1956c26a6","tid":909834,"uid":175598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:42:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"512cd881e0299ac6a310f85ee7fb5e9728d89cca","tid":909834,"uid":200521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"To 含大仔:<br />\n中國有一句話叫：「悶聲大發財」，這是最後的！<br />\n咪撚再衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e41fb9529fc0d3878b148806e75ef672f583a21","tid":909834,"uid":200521,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockqu